###Configure data source for Windows

1. Start a PowerShell session.
2. Navigate to the Edge System installation directory: %Program Files%/OSIsoft/EdgeSystem.
3. To configure a data source, run this command.

   ...
.\OSIsoft.Data.System.Host.exe configuration ConnectivityComponentID DataSource Url=opc tcp://localhost:5463/SimulationServer
   ...
   
4. To view configured data sources and help, run this command:

   ...
.\OSIsoft.Data.System.Host.exe configuration ConnectivityComponentID DataSource
   ...
